{"tid":1643944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依家既宵禁係香港人自己做出黎","createTime":"2019-10-10T11:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T11:07:49.000Z","uid":269433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"58e79c3a309af285f1600e02faacbb85692f326d","tid":1643944,"uid":269433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:03:19.000Z","msg":"依家8、9點後條街冇曬人, 重有咩資格話要遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前口口聲聲話唔搭, 跳閘時期 平均一日都冇見到一個人跳<br />\n發生左咁多件事 你重忍到黨鐵?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">裝修</span>果時又咁踴躍?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反共、反中資</span>唔撚係講笑</span><br />\n<br />\n你地重依賴黨鐵? 冇黨鐵唔撚會死架, 依家既宵禁係香港人自己做出黎, 黨鐵幾點停就幾點前返屋企on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴士出黎撐左咁多次<br />\n記唔記得<span style=\"color: gold;\">8．5</span>佢地點封路?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">罷買</span>?   <span style=\"color: gold;\">懲罰</span>?</span><br />\n要進化要遍地開花. 唔該先唔好再依賴黨鐵<br />\n和勇不分唔係講係要做出黎<br />\n你地願意每次都200萬人出黎我相信比你派再多物資更有用.<br />\n呢2張圖已經等於黨鐵 (<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拋磚引玉歡迎巴絲提供更多搭車方法)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2sJK35U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2sJK35U.jpg&h=cda1a4b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnqxtxA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnqxtxA.jpg&h=e25bbfae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人！反抗!</span><br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n和勇相鏈 反抗極權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"5d4bf49232813eaa7769358359beed5f27769a0e","tid"